def max_sum_of_diameters(test_cases):
    results = []
    for case in test_cases:
        N = case['N']
        A = case['A']
        B = case['B']
        A.sort()
        B.sort()
        s = 1
        for i in range(N):
            s += min(A[i], B[i])
        results.append(s)
    return results
